tical-listening and psychoacoustic interpretation rules. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-| MPC-014 | Encode SenseWeave voice-to-music interpretation rules. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-| MPC-015 | Implement ensemble-space and Theramini partner behavior from the course. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-| MPC-016 | Add a genre-literacy strategy library. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-| MPC-017 | Make the 30-minute production score executable. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-| MPC-018 | Add phase-transition composition techniques. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-| MPC-019 | Build SuperCollider recipe references without coupling tests to live audio. | SHOULD | T2 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-| MPC-020 | Wire production-course choices into score trees and tracker output. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-| MPC-021 | Extend the composition gate with production-course checks. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-| MPC-022 | Add course-driven self-critique and revision targets. | SHOULD | T2 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-| MPC-023 | Turn the production course into executable curriculum exercises. | SHOULD | T2 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-| MPC-024 | Add operator diagnostics for production-course decisions. | SHOULD | T2 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-| MPC-025 | Add end-to-end production-course integration tests. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\ No newline at end of file\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-001 | Implement the Event dataclass with score-level, performance-level, reactive-delta, and provenance fields. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-002 | Implement PerformanceIntent per-phrase metadata with arc shape, deviation bounds, tension target, restraint, and call/response role. | MUST | T1 |